Body:
It is He who sends down water from the skies; you drink thereof,
			and thereof [drink] the plants upon which you pasture your
			beasts;

For, should you try to count God's blessings, you could never
			compute them! Behold, God is indeed much-forgiving, a dispenser
			of grace;

And [consider how] thy Sustainer has inspired the bee:<span class='fn'>77</span>
			"Prepare for thyself dwellings in mountains and in trees, and in
			what [men] may build [for thee by way of hives];
